Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.76,0:00:13.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家好  我是平泽忧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.43,0:00:17.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天是我和小梓第一次一起出门
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.31,0:00:20.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.93,0:00:22.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  小梓
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.70,0:00:25.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.17,0:00:29.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,衣服好可爱啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.21,0:00:34.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  这次轻音部也要去合宿吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.79,0:00:36.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  去四天三夜
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.38,0:00:41.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去年呢  姐姐说非常开心哦
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.90,0:00:43.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,开心？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.43,0:00:48.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  那是指练习得很充实吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.74,0:00:50.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎？嗯…嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.03,0:00:52.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,应该是吧…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.88,0:00:54.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  忧～
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.25,0:00:56.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很可爱吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.24,0:00:58.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.55,0:01:01.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家可是奏出那么动听音乐的前辈呢
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.55,0:01:04.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,合宿这种程度的事…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.07,0:01:07.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没问题吧…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.11,0:02:45.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姐姐在轻音部里是怎样的呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.95,0:02:47.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯…嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.69,0:02:48.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,稍微有点那个啦
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.01,0:02:49.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么什么
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.23,0:02:54.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一点也不练习  还取奇怪的外号
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.17,0:02:57.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,动不动就在我身上蹭来蹭去
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.35,0:02:57.86,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,梓喵  好软好软～
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.05,0:03:00.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姐姐她很暖很舒服吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.97,0:03:03.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不  不是那个意思…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.38,0:03:04.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.71,0:03:06.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天唯前辈在干什么呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.18,0:03:08.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,家里蹲着呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.43,0:03:12.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姐姐很怕热  但又讨厌空调
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.43,0:03:12.58,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊～  好热好热～
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.87,0:03:15.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我能看见她懒塌塌的样子了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.37,0:03:17.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最近每天都是精疲力尽的样子呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.44,0:03:20.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是不像样子啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.40,0:03:24.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是  滚来滚去的姐姐好可爱哦～
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.41,0:03:26.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,忧～  忧～
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.52,0:03:28.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到底是什么呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.58,0:03:30.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我和忧这感觉的差别
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.51,0:03:36.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我比较希望有个像澪前辈这样的姐姐呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.35,0:03:39.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,澪学姐又温柔又帅气哦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.22,0:03:41.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,律学姐呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.46,0:03:43.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.32,0:03:46.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个人马马虎虎且粗枝大叶的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.88,0:03:48.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,忽略掉…吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.41,0:03:49.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦～
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.49,0:03:51.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你说谁粗枝大叶啊  
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.16,0:03:52.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哇！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.00,0:03:57.96,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起…对不起…对不起…对不起…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.75,0:03:54.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,律学姐好
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.18,0:03:56.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呀呵～
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.19,0:03:57.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在外面看见你们就进来了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.35,0:03:59.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天就一个人吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.22,0:04:02.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  澪参加暑期讲学去了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.26,0:04:05.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,律前辈你不去也行吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.91,0:04:09.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎  我么？ 暑期讲学？为啥？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.65,0:04:12.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,…也是呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.97,0:04:15.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  说起来有件事我一直很在意
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.35,0:04:16.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.37,0:04:22.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,前辈又是自己带茶具  又有别墅
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.35,0:04:24.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是个很有钱的大小姐吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.49,0:04:27.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对哦  她家里还有管家
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.50,0:04:30.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,放长假经常去外国的哦～
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.72,0:04:31.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的吗？！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.00,0:04:33.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那样就很有趣了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.21,0:04:36.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你瞎说的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.81,0:04:40.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么  现在打个电话找去家里玩吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.16,0:04:42.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好吗  这么突然…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.57,0:04:49.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎  不接电话啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.94,0:04:51.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打她家里吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.10,0:04:58.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你好
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.21,0:05:00.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打通了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.45,0:05:02.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  请问是同学的父亲吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.11,0:05:06.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不  我是琴吹家的管家
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.82,0:05:08.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真有管家啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.51,0:05:12.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那…那个  同学在家吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.22,0:05:13.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,前辈  冷静
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.94,0:05:18.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大小姐现在正在芬兰避暑
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.95,0:05:21.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样啊  非常感谢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.43,0:05:22.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我先挂了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.79,0:05:27.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你看  我说得没错吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.39,0:05:28.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦～
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.11,0:05:32.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊…感觉好累啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.55,0:05:35.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要来我家转一圈吗  有西瓜哦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.53,0:05:36.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.26,0:05:38.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我回来了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.91,0:05:39.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.15,0:05:40.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,西瓜…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.05,0:05:43.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,律学姐和小梓来了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.25,0:05:47.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,欢～迎～回～来～
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.68,0:05:52.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一看她我真放心啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.77,0:05:54.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人如其闻啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.56,0:05:55.02,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哈～  好可爱～
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.66,0:05:58.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打扰了～
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.58,0:06:00.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  她在她在
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.80,0:06:04.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然是暑假  但真够辛苦啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.01,0:06:07.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,研修什么的都撞在一起了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.92,0:06:09.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们也要练习吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.65,0:06:10.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.50,0:06:11.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有事吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.60,0:06:13.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,轻音部要搞合宿
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.08,0:06:16.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想问问老师你要不要来
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.75,0:06:18.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,合宿啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.49,0:06:20.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,唔哈哈…一副麻烦死了的表情
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.24,0:06:24.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那算了  我们自己去好了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.52,0:06:26.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不跟你打招呼就生气  
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.29,0:06:27.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跟你说了又这副样子
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.93,0:06:30.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又能游泳又能烧烤呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.88,0:06:33.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哇  真是好期待啊  合宿
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.06,0:06:38.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好～
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.93,0:06:41.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家好久没聚在一起了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.36,0:06:43.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一起去为合宿购物吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.73,0:06:47.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,话说回来  要买点什么呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.19,0:06:49.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,新的器材吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.10,0:06:51.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.77,0:06:52.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,泳装哦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.69,0:06:53.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,玩心十足啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.09,0:06:56.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,反正我想也是这么回事
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.77,0:06:58.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也不是一直都玩嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.98,0:07:00.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谁上你的当啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.49,0:07:01.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为啥？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.21,0:07:03.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总之  休息也是必要的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.86,0:07:04.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.70,0:07:08.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗…也是呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.67,0:07:12.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这份孤独感是什么呢…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.31,0:07:16.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦哦哦～
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.37,0:07:18.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这又强大了一级啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.76,0:07:22.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这就是去年说的没借到的别墅吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.36,0:07:23.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.46,0:07:26.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个别墅今年也不行
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.57,0:07:29.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多少有点挤  请大家忍耐下
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.69,0:07:31.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还有更大的啊！？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.18,0:07:34.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好  去玩喽！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.63,0:07:36.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦～！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.24,0:07:37.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂—！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.14,0:07:39.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,给我练完再去玩
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.25,0:07:40.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎～
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.16,0:07:42.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人家想玩！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.93,0:07:44.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么投票决定吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.05,0:07:46.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要先练习
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.61,0:07:47.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,玩！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.59,0:07:48.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,练习比较好
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.90,0:07:52.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想玩～
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.66,0:07:54.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,意料之外的背叛！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.57,0:07:55.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快点
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.80,0:07:56.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.95,0:08:00.81,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的  把玩也算进前期事项的话…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.68,0:08:01.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是  前辈的玩难道是…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.09,0:08:05.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I am flying！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.66,0:08:07.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Yes，Yes Yes！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.09,0:08:07.53,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,（笔头调：Here we go！！）
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.43,0:08:10.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不会的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.96,0:08:18.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我说过不要的嘛！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.36,0:08:20.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快把海滨的东西收拾掉  
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.95,0:08:22.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,游艇也不要！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.44,0:08:23.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.21,0:08:23.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,前辈
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.08,0:08:26.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看招～
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.56,0:08:27.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊哈哈哈哈～
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.14,0:08:31.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊哈哈哈哈…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.24,0:08:33.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊哈哈哈哈…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.44,0:08:35.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嘿咻  嘿咻～
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.96,0:08:38.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能好好练习吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.59,0:08:39.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,梓喵～
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.67,0:08:43.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,梓喵也来一起玩吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.95,0:08:44.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不用了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.72,0:08:47.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难道说你不擅长运动？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.04,0:08:50.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没…没有这回事！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.52,0:08:51.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,玩给你看！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.10,0:09:01.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小梓已经和大家相处得很好了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.64,0:09:03.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.98,0:09:08.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小律博士  请看这个
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.82,0:09:09.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,澪前辈
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.92,0:09:10.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.41,0:09:14.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你知道藤壶的故事吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.11,0:09:17.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以前有位因藤壶而划破腿的少年…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.11,0:09:17.99,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,（都市传说「藤壶与膝盖」，参考第四话）
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.90,0:09:20.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊…那个…澪前…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.21,0:09:23.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,…辈？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.20,0:09:27.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没到没到还在前面哦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.82,0:09:28.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还差点
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.46,0:09:29.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,上啊上啊～
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.26,0:09:31.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了～
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.33,0:09:36.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,给我来一口
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.31,0:09:36.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.24,0:09:38.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,澪
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.07,0:09:43.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊哈哈哈哈  我这个人啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.81,0:09:57.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里是？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.88,0:10:01.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,无人岛…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.96,0:10:06.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小律
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.88,0:10:11.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,唯…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.49,0:10:17.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,唯…唯！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.79,0:10:19.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小律
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.09,0:10:23.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,终于到了…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.60,0:10:25.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,新大陆啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.15,0:10:27.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Zipangu！  
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.32,0:10:28.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,黄金之岛～
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.32,0:10:28.88,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,（Zipangu：见4话注释）
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.62,0:10:28.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们在干什么…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.06,0:10:31.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呼
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.37,0:10:32.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,玩爽了玩爽了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.18,0:10:35.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,差不多吃个饭洗洗睡吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.69,0:10:36.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,练习怎么办呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.36,0:10:41.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然应该不玩先练习才对
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.97,0:10:44.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,梓才是玩得最欢的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.25,0:10:45.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都晒黑了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.16,0:10:48.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我可是会好好练习的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.36,0:10:49.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么  练一整晚？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.54,0:10:52.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,练就练！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.95,0:10:58.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,K-ON!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.02,0:11:02.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,累死了～
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.49,0:11:03.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,饿死了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.01,0:11:04.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,忍忍吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.72,0:11:09.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好棒～
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.51,0:11:13.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,的确了不得
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.20,0:11:16.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我还从没用过那样的扩音器
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.70,0:11:18.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,澪！快来练习吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.90,0:11:20.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这鼓竟然是全新的！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.46,0:11:21.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,万恶的拜金主义者
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.86,0:11:26.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,梓喵  那个是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.95,0:11:28.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  这个吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.19,0:11:30.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是个调音器
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.05,0:11:33.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎  这个叫调音器啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.19,0:11:33.71,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,（调音器（tuner）：校正音高或给予标准音高的工具）
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.96,0:11:35.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是用这个来调音的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.44,0:11:39.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,唯前辈你不知道调音器的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.46,0:11:41.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  头一次见
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.69,0:11:43.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那你以前都是怎么调音的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.63,0:11:47.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,适当的…你看
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.97,0:11:50.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,绝…绝对音感！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.82,0:11:53.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真不知道这个人是废柴还是强人
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.94,0:11:55.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我们来吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.62,0:11:58.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,one two three four
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.63,0:12:07.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刚才这曲感觉很好呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.28,0:12:09.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很合拍呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.37,0:12:11.55,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太棒了  小唯
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.97,0:12:13.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家都是什么时候练习的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.35,0:12:13.68,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没啦没啦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.93,0:12:16.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,律你的鼓点打得挺准的嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.72,0:12:18.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,自己特训过吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.35,0:12:23.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,饿死我了…没劲儿了…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.17,0:12:27.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为肚子饿所以没有多余的力气乱敲了吗…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.40,0:12:30.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去吃饭吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.76,0:12:33.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让我吃饭～！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.81,0:12:35.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也是
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.19,0:12:37.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我回来啦～
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.96,0:12:39.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,欢迎回来
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.38,0:12:40.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们回来了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.52,0:12:43.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小律！有肉有菜哦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.93,0:12:45.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我等好久啦！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.81,0:12:49.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,圆圆的卷心菜！看我一口生吞下去！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.95,0:12:51.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,给我忍忍
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.36,0:12:54.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,成天看她们在玩
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.03,0:12:56.01,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,忍无可忍！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.59,0:12:57.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但演奏的时候为什么就那么顺畅呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.44,0:12:59.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,松手！卷心菜之…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.81,0:13:02.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家分工合作马上就能做好了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.25,0:13:02.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,卷心菜之神要生气了！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.26,0:13:05.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我去看看炉火
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.28,0:13:09.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看  学妹都率先表态了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.17,0:13:11.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,知道了啦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.82,0:13:16.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,眼睛好疼
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.37,0:13:18.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,唯  没事吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.84,0:13:20.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小律
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.50,0:13:22.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,唯
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.32,0:13:24.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们死也要死在一起
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.74,0:13:25.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.62,0:13:31.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好  那我们来做饭团吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.70,0:13:32.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.16,0:13:42.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,差距竟然这么大…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.06,0:13:47.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是不是小澪的手太大了呀？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.49,0:13:48.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,闭嘴！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.32,0:14:08.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊～好好吃啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.07,0:14:10.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,的确很好吃
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.53,0:14:11.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真赞啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.26,0:14:14.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我们来放烟花吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.22,0:14:30.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.58,0:14:32.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最后要烧完的时候
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.07,0:14:35.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,心里总会念着让它再加把劲再加把劲这样吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.21,0:14:38.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再加把劲～  再加把劲～
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.66,0:14:39.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.08,0:14:43.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好  再来一根
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.49,0:14:46.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再加把劲  再加把劲
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.39,0:14:51.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又掉了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.80,0:14:55.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小律  要灭啦…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.66,0:14:58.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没问题！这种时候就要进行合体巨大化！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.65,0:15:01.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,合体！ 线香花火人！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.13,0:15:03.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  不带这样的…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.91,0:15:04.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,笨啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.54,0:15:06.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,重不重？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.69,0:15:07.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没问题
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.13,0:15:09.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来开试胆大会吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.59,0:15:10.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦～
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.70,0:15:12.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还没完没了了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.48,0:15:13.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.51,0:15:15.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说到夏天和合宿的话  
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.44,0:15:16.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么可以没有试胆大会
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.82,0:15:18.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我可不参加
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.19,0:15:19.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对啦～
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.16,0:15:22.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,澪怕鬼故事呢～
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.25,0:15:24.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,完全没问题
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.91,0:15:26.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来就来谁怕你
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.49,0:15:30.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,之前不让我好好吃饭的仇
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.41,0:15:31.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这回要让你一次还清
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.02,0:15:43.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都…都是高中生了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.22,0:15:45.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还搞什么试胆大会啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.83,0:15:48.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个…我的手很疼…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.90,0:15:53.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那…那是什么…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.47,0:15:55.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一…一…一…一定…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.35,0:15:57.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是律…律…律在搞鬼
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.79,0:16:10.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小澪…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.61,0:16:14.07,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好怕！  好可怕！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.42,0:16:14.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,前辈！前辈！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.55,0:16:15.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请保持镇定！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.16,0:16:19.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老…老师？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.81,0:16:20.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你这是怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.58,0:16:23.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,终…终于见到你们了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.21,0:16:26.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦？ 小佐和老师？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.40,0:16:27.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你怎么了？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.54,0:16:28.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说来你怎么在这里？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.60,0:16:35.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我本打算晚点和大家汇合  吓你们一跳的…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.78,0:16:37.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,结果迷路了…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.90,0:16:42.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过我看吓人这个目的倒是达到了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.45,0:16:45.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小澪！没事了！小澪！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.68,0:16:48.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,澪前辈原来这么怕的啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.44,0:16:57.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么没人来
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.87,0:17:03.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是吓死人了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.56,0:17:04.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,算啦算啦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.42,0:17:05.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,澪～澪
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.00,0:17:13.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,梓  你怕热吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.41,0:17:16.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不  倒也不是
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.85,0:17:20.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,梓喵  这时候最好要一口气沉下去啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.02,0:17:23.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,疼！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.03,0:17:25.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被太阳晒的很疼吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.33,0:17:27.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,唯你瘦了点吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.68,0:17:31.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有  以前也说过吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.39,0:17:34.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不管吃多少都长不胖的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.58,0:17:35.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,羡慕死你了！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.90,0:17:38.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦  连小佐和老师也？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.83,0:17:40.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.83,0:17:45.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一摘下眼镜就分不太清楚你们两个人了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.22,0:17:52.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用胸部大小来判断不就行了嘛～
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.09,0:17:53.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊哈★
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.16,0:18:07.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,稠状的…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.86,0:18:09.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,卷心菜真好吃～
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.80,0:18:33.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好意思  让你来陪我练习
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.50,0:18:35.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请不用放在心上
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.81,0:18:40.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也想和唯前辈在一起多多练习
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.73,0:18:41.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.54,0:18:43.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.14,0:19:00.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,梓喵你好厉害哦～
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.95,0:19:03.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没什么了不得的啦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.81,0:19:06.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那下来轮到我了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.86,0:19:16.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这块很难啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.55,0:19:19.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,开始先用慢速来弹就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.04,0:19:20.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.08,0:19:38.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,弹出来了！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.51,0:19:41.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,认识梓喵太好啦！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.23,0:19:44.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,梓喵～
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.59,0:19:49.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢你  梓喵
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.23,0:20:06.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家好  我是平泽忧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.89,0:20:09.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天也和小梓一起出门
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.04,0:20:10.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.41,0:20:16.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起  来晚了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.58,0:20:18.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的  好慢啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.47,0:20:19.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦…谁啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.89,0:20:25.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没能怎么练习吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.17,0:20:27.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也不是没有练…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.93,0:20:30.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是想要再特训下的…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.97,0:20:32.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可却跑去游泳啊试胆大会啊什么的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.19,0:20:34.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,几乎一直在玩
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.91,0:20:37.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是想多练习的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.18,0:20:39.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.63,0:20:42.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是姐姐完全没有晒黑啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.99,0:20:44.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你为什么晒成这样呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.42,0:20:46.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这…这个…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.69,0:20:50.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为我就是玩得最欢的那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.16,0:20:54.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过呢…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.77,0:21:00.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我还是觉得能去合宿真的挺好
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.91,0:21:05.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还了解了不少前辈她们的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.87,0:21:07.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦  什么样的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.34,0:21:12.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯…澪前辈其实挺胆小的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.78,0:21:13.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.43,0:21:15.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,律学姐呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.97,0:21:17.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然还是挺粗枝大叶的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.43,0:21:20.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过和澪前辈的感情挺不错的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.10,0:21:22.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,学姐呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.64,0:21:24.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,前辈啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.77,0:21:27.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,尽管平时很照顾大家
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.38,0:21:29.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想不到也有很孩子气的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.55,0:21:30.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是个很可爱的人呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.18,0:21:32.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯～
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.65,0:21:34.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我姐姐呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.01,0:21:37.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,唯前辈呢…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.83,0:21:41.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在好好练习了！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.86,0:21:42.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对吧～
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.63,0:21:54.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.27,0:22:02.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她还是会冲上来抱着我呢
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.46,0:22:04.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姐姐暖暖的对不对
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.34,0:22:08.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嘿嘿…算是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.92,0:23:43.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,唔…琴弦都生锈了嘛！
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.28,0:23:46.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你上次换弦是什么时候？
Dialogue: 0,0:23:47.07,0:23:49.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诶？弦能换的吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:23:51.03,0:23:52.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什…什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:23:52.75,0:23:54.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个…是经典吉他吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:23:55.40,0:23:58.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起…就是脏了点…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:58.38,0:24:00.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,才刚买了一年
Dialogue: 0,0:24:00.45,0:24:03.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果她真就这么走掉的话
Dialogue: 0,0:24:04.74,0:24:08.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,学园祭的演出  要怎么办呢
Dialogue: 0,0:24:06.15,0:24:09.66,title2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,0)}#11　　危机!


